FBIS4-65195 "drweu093_h_94003" FBIS-WEU-94-093 Daily Report 12 May 1994 GERMANY Russian Minister Approves Farewell in Berlin Russian Minister Approves Farewell in Berlin AU1205134794 Cologne Deutschlandfunk Network in German 0900 GMT 12 May 94 AU1205134794 Cologne Deutschlandfunk Network German BFN [Text] Russian Defense Minister Grachev has expressed his satisfaction with the compromise solution for the organization of the withdrawal of his troops from Germany. It is important that Chancellor Kohl assesses the mood in Russia correctly and has agreed to a ceremony in Berlin, he said.
